      "code_id": "ceab8f51-599e-430e-8ffb-703e92ebab2f",
      "code_content": "def fibonacci(n):\n    if n <= 1:\n        return n\n    else:\n        return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2)\n\n\nn = int(input())\nresult = fibonacci(n)\nprint(result)\n",
